What I need you to do to set up for the new season:

Replace FULL_SCHEDULE in index.html — fetch the complete 2026-27 schedule for all 32 teams from the NHL API (https://api-web.nhle.com/v1/club-schedule-season/{TEAM}/now) and format it as the FULL_SCHEDULE object. Keep the same format: {"NYI": [["Oct 9", "OPP", "H"], ...], ...} for all 32 teams.
